      "source_title": "HealthPlix Technologies — Full-Stack Software Engineer — EHR Platform",
      "text": "Full-Stack Software Engineer — EHR Platform at HealthPlix Technologies (Apr 2021 — Dec 2023). Built MedAssist and CareCoordinator, EHR products used by clinicians across partner hospital networks — backend services, React frontends, and FHIR integrations. Built prescription + SOAP note modules in Django — 2M+ monthly prescriptions at 99.9% uptime Took API response times from 420ms to 95ms via PostgreSQL query optimization and index tuning Migrated a monolithic patient-record service to event-driven RabbitMQ — decoupled 5 consumers Integrated FHIR R4 across 3 partner hospital networks — 65% less manual data sync Stack: Python, Django, React, TypeScript, PostgreSQL, RabbitMQ, Redis, ELK, GitHub Actions.",
